No. 53,

Misc.

Bachellar et al. v. Maryland. Fred E. Weisgal and Anthony G. Amsterdam for petitioners. Francis B. Burch, Attorney General of Maryland, and Edward F. Borgerding and H. Edgar Lentz, Assistant Attorneys General, for respondent.

Ct. Sp. App. Md. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted and case transferred to appellate docket.
